.1392940>10.3389/fimmu.2024.1392940</a></p></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><guid ispermalink="false">发布：39015576</guid><pubDate> Wed, 17 Jul 2024 06:00:00 -0400</pubDate><dc:creator>吴浩东</dc:creator><dc:creator>吴志轩</dc:creator><dc:creator>李红峰</dc:creator><dc:creator>王自琼</dc:creator><dc:creator>姚晨</dc:creator><dc:creator>鲍静霞</dc:creator><dc:creator>陈布兰</dc:creator><dc:creator>徐淑宁</dc:creator><dc:creator>夏二杰</dc:creator><dc:creator>呆脚叶</dc:creator><dc:creator>戴轩轩</dc:creator><dc:date>2024-07-17</dc:date><dc:source>免疫学前沿</dc:source><dc:title>利用机器学习进行基于糖基磷脂酰肌醇锚定生物合成途径的生物标志物识别，用于乳腺癌的预后和 T 细胞耗竭状态预测</dc:title><dc:identifier>下午：39015576</dc:identifier><dc:identifier>管理中心：PMC11249538</dc:identifier><dc:identifier> doi:10.3389/fimmu.2024.1392940</dc:identifier></item></channel></rss>